clientX/Y：相较于浏览器窗口 elem.getBoundingClientRect()
pageX/Y：相较于文档的位置 elem.getBoundingClientRect() + 页面滚动

elem.getBoundingClientRect() 返回元素相较于窗口的坐标

document.documentElement.clientHeight 获取当前浏览器的高度

left = x
top = y
right = x+width(offsetWidth)
bottom = y+height(offsetHeight)

pageY = clientY + window.pageYOffset
pageX = clientX + window.pageXOffset



